+def fibonacci(n):
+    if n <= 0:
+        return []
+    elif n == 1:
+        return [0]
+
+    sequence = [0, 1]
+    while len(sequence) < n:
+        sequence.append(sequence[-1] + sequence[-2])
+    return sequence
+
+# Print first 10 Fibonacci numbers
+print(fibonacci(10))
